li>\r<li>Fixed &#8220;settings&#8221; link on plugins page when network activated.</li>\r<li>Added new menu page for File Manager options.</li>\r<li>Finalized language translation strings.</li>\r<li>Added tabs for options administration (settings page).</li>\r<li>Added multiple options for controlling various parts of the File Manager configuration.</li>\r<li>Added options for allowable file types.</li>\r<li>Added auto-update code; so future updates can be administered via the WP panel.</li>\r</ul>\r<h3>Add Media Button Update</h3>\r<p>A few new options have also been added to the &#8220;Editor&#8221; tab.</p>\r<p>These options apply to the &#8220;Add Media&#8221; button; just above the content editor.</p>\r<p>Options can now be set to control the default values used for media alignment, link and type.</p>\r<div id=\"attachment_1622\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/wpeditpro/~https://wpeditpro.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/add_media3.png\"><img src=\"https://wpeditpro.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/add_media3.png\" alt=\"WP Edit Pro Add Media Options\" width=\"608\" height=\"269\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1622\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">WP Edit Pro Add Media Options</p></div>\r<div style=\"margin-top:20px;\"></div>\r<div id=\"attachment_1616\" style=\"width: 302px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/wpeditpro/~https://wpeditpro.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/add_media2.png\"><img src=\"https://wpeditpro.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/add_media2.png\" alt=\"Add Media Attachment Settings\" width=\"292\" height=\"243\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1616\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Add Media Attachment Settings</p></div>\r<div style=\"margin-top:20px;\"></div>\r<Img align=\"left\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:0;float:left;margin:0;padding:0\" hspace=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/i/87451031/0/wpeditpr